comments: Aldridge (SAS) cleanly dislodges the ball from Bridges (PHX).
Booker (PHX) does not maintain verticality and he makes contact to Aldridge's (SAS) arm that affects his shot near the rim.
Ayton (PHX) and Aldridge (SAS) briefly engage and disengage as they fight for off ball position.
Forbes (SAS) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Saric (PHX) in the post.
DeRozan (SAS) legally contests Bridges' (PHX) jump shot attempt.
Bridges (PHX) is moving alongside DeRozan's (SAS) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he defends the drive to the basket.
Mills (SAS) steps out of bounds and does not re-establish himself back in bounds prior to making contact with the ball.
Mills (SAS) cleanly steals the ball from Ayton (PHX).
Oubre Jr. (PHX) is already in Aldridge's (SAS) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Forbes (SAS) legally contests Oubre Jr.'s (PHX) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Oubre Jr. (PHX) legally contests Mills' (SAS) jump shot attempt.
Rubio (PHX) first holds/impedes Mills then wraps Aldridge (SAS) pulloing him back into Mills affecting the FOM of Mills.
Walker IV (SAS) commits a take foul on Bridges (PHX).
Rubio (PHX) places his hand momentarily on Mills' (SAS) hip before correcting.
Rubio (PHX) is moving alongside DeRozan's (SAS) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he defends the drive to the basket.
Mills (SAS) extends his leg and makes marginal contact with Ayton (PHX), who would avoid making contact with Mills if not for the leg extension.
Aldridge (SAS) commits a take foul on Bridges (PHX).
